Orckit Gains First Time in Four Days on ‘Buy’ Recommendation

-- B y   R o n i t   G o o d m a n
-- 
2011-03-13T15:24:35Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-13/orckit-gains-first-time-in-four-days-on-buy-recommendation-1-.html
  Orckit Communications Ltd. (ORCT)  advanced
for the first time in four days after the Israeli maker of
telecommunications equipment was rated new “buy” with a price
estimate of $4.50 per share at Roth Capital Partners LLC.  The shares rose 3.6 percent to 9.744 shekels at the 4:30
p.m. close in  Tel Aviv , giving the company a market value of
219.1 million shekels ($61 million).  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ronit Goodman in Tel Aviv at 
 rgoodman9@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Claudia Maedler at 
 cmaedler@bloomberg.net  